The China Degradable Chelator market size was valued at US$ 278.5 million in 2024 and is projected to reach US$ 423.6 million by 2030, at a CAGR of 7.2% during the forecast period 2024-2030.

Degradable Chelators are environmentally friendly complexing agents that break down naturally in the environment, used in various applications including cleaning products, water treatment, and personal care to replace traditional, persistent chelators.

